01:35:00.920 --> 01:35:02.251
(HURLEMENT)

01:35:13.280 --> 01:35:15.965
(GRONDEMENT)

01:35:22.920 --> 01:35:24.365
(CHRISTINE HALEINE)

01:35:26.560 --> 01:35:27.971
(CRIS)

01:35:28.800 --> 01:35:29.961
Avril!

01:35:40.600 --> 01:35:43.251
(BRUIT CASSANT)

